---
title: Caribbean Beef Rissoles & Avocado Slaw with Charred Corn & Baby Leaves
description: Charred corn is the perfect addition to a colourful slaw, it's juicy and sweet. Keep tastiness going by spicing the beef rissoles in a Caribbean jerk seasoning. It’s a dish that leaves a pleasant, warm feeling after you're done.

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66d94ffd5a192a1abc1ee321-f89af6cb.jpeg
